data.description: Located in quiet Ashton Heights, just minutes from Langley and Route 64, this home is a 1970s gem. A refreshed kitchen with butcher block countertops provides plenty of space for the chef(s), while others can hang out in the den or the spacious living room. Upstairs, there are four generous bedrooms, one with an ensuite, and an updated hall bathroom. Don't forget the sizable 2-car garage and the 0.27-acre backyard. A few photos have been virtually staged. Call/text now to schedule your own showing!
